Fostering collaboration on Sustainable_Agriculture , Food and Energy which will be held from 17-20 November 2015 at Nong_Lam_University_Ho_Chi_Minh_City , VIETNAM . This conference is the third conference after the 1st International_Conference on Sustainable_Agriculture , Food , and Energy ( SAFE2013 ) in Padang , Indonesia ( 12-14 May 2013 ) and the 2nd conference SAFE2014 in Bali , Indonesia ( 17-19 September 2014 ) .
